wellcom: Welcome to the virtual training application
list_des_b1:
> The 4-stroke 3V Euro 3 125 engine with electronic fuel injection maximizes fuel efficiency and achieves a 50% noise reduction.
> The wheel size is 12 inches and is equipped with an ABS anti-lock braking system.
list_des_b2:
> Three sharp air intakes designed for a sporty appearance.
> The body is covered with sound-absorbing material to reduce mechanical noise.
> Can be connected to smart devices via Bluetooth.
list_des_b3:
> Standard start/stop feature automatically stops the engine to save fuel.
> There is a large under-seat storage space with a capacity of 36.2 liters.
list_des_b4:
> Iconic style, vibrant colors. Safety is enhanced with a completely redesigned suspension system.
> Keyless, convenient USB port, and many other new features.
